Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.96,0:11:14.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们总是走不到能通车的路呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.88,0:11:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就在这过夜如何？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.96,0:11:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌 你还好吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.74,0:11:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真是没用…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.14,0:11:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有这回事咧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.44,0:11:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不不…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.14,0:11:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果麻幌你不在这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.94,0:11:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是这样的 阿优
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.00,0:11:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这时候有点对不起阿优 可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.53,0:11:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说咧…\n我觉得我现在很高兴…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.92,0:11:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没有总部那些人的协助 \n就会变得很无助…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.56,0:11:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.26,0:11:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感到我能做到目前这样…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.70,0:11:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都是因为有周围的人在支持与鼓励
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.16,0:12:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 对我来说…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.50,0:12:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是麻幌一个人也已经帮了我很多忙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.59,0:12:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要的只是你一直陪伴在我身边…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.94,0:12:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光是那样我就满足了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:13.98,0:12:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还记得麻幌跟我去横滨的约会吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.68,0:12:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！那时候式条老师一直纠缠着我们真是麻烦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.71,0:12:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可是那倒帮了我一个大忙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.87,0:12:27.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,约会的时候我一直很不自在…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那让我觉得有一点背悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.36,0:12:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然会觉得害羞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.30,0:12:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直看着对方时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.81,0:12:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二人之间的一切似乎都消失了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.52,0:12:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失得过头突然变得害怕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.59,0:12:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我东张西望看看周围…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是 当我再转过头看她的时候…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她会不在原来的地方了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:52.52,0:12:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这种感觉…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.99,0:13:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.06,0:13:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这附近有海！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.59,0:13:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,海…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:52.45,0:13:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美里司令曾经告诉我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.88,0:13:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这世界上有更美丽的事物…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.00,0:14:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更美丽的事物？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.39,0:14:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我终于知道那是什么了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是跟你喜欢的人\n一起看着的夕阳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.07,0:14:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯真的呢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.52,0:14:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天快要黑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.39,0:15:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 那个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.76,0:15:05.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻…幌…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.50,0:15:07.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.69,0:15:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.56,0:15:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们现在处于很紧急的状况 \n不应该做那种事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.01,0:15:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么？\n换上战斗服有什么不对的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.33,0:15:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚上的森林是很危险的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.56,0:15:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到天亮之前我会一直保护你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.30,0:15:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呃 是这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.16,0:15:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.51,0:15:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…你怎么找到这里的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.33,0:15:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你吃惊了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.80,0:15:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.91,0:15:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心 我得兴趣不是偷袭你们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.35,0:15:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是说这个！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.06,0:15:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,偷看女生换衣服是没常识的人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.46,0:15:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.56,0:15:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起对不起 我正巧路过这
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…透过追踪你的领针
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.88,0:16:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我早就该发觉这点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.77,0:16:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.99,0:16:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你没事吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.54,0:16:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…只是树枝碰到脸而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.15,0:16:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算我可以和贝鲁德拉斯战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.94,0:16:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我不可能同时保护阿优…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.75,0:16:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我现在该怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.89,0:16:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他没有跟着我们过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.40,0:16:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有人说过攻击就是最好的防御
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.37,0:17:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌？你要做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.79,0:17:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优 请跑得越远越好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.62,0:17:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要击倒贝鲁德拉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.42,0:17:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌她要离开我了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.62,0:17:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌她要离开我了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.82,0:17:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.27,0:17:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不！你不可以这样走了！\n你说过你哪里都不去的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.02,0:17:27.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说过会永远跟我在一起的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.89,0:17:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎样 你都会永远跟我在一起不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.95,0:17:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.71,0:17:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阿优…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.81,0:17:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远跟你在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.93,0:18:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道离这有多远
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.34,0:18:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是只要你一直沿着海岸往南走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.72,0:18:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该会碰到一个叫做坎比齐的港都
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.76,0:18:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们就约在那碰面吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一定要来喔！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.22,0:18:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.44,0:18:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.17,0:18:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果这是个陷阱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.54,0:18:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕美里优早就死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.49,0:18:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从来没想过这点吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.58,0:18:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你从来就没有打算要等到我的机能停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.73,0:18:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一开始的目的就是要跟我战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.73,0:18:52.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是这样\n你刚刚就不会跟踪我们到这了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:53.27,0:18:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.48,0:18:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然你和我是不同的造型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们都是只为了战斗而存在的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.66,0:19:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是有趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.74,0:19:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这武器似乎能无限制地变强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.14,0:20:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像地球也变成两半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.49,0:20:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道这武器的真正使用方法！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.06,0:20:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.89,0:20:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻幌！麻…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.98,0:23:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(276,250)\fs24\fad(1200,4000)}往最终话…
