Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.12,0:23:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从前有个男人离乡背井
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:47.28,0:23:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,流浪到外国的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.23,0:23:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爱上的当地的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.07,0:23:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己在那边建立酿酒厂\n然后在那里做起生意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.93,0:23:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酿酒厂帮男人立了家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.12,0:23:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人就造了自己出生的故乡的酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.08,0:24:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那酒实在太过华丽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.06,0:24:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以致不像男人故乡的任何一种酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.91,0:24:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(116,203)\fs18\fnsimhei\bord0\shad0\1c&Hffffff&\fade(255,0,0,0,1500,6200,7700)}最终话
